---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "src/layouts/Layout.astro";
import people from "src/assets/images/people-smiling.jpg";
---

<Layout title="About us">
  <section>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 py-20 max-md:py-10 px-2">
      <Image
        class="w-96 max-md:w-72"
        src={people}
        alt="Astro logo"
        width={500}
        height={500}
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-8">
        <h1 class="capitalize text-center text-6xl font-bold max-md:text-4xl">
          Meet Adele - The Heart Behind Our Gym
        </h1>
        <div class="w-1/2 mx-auto mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl mb-3">Embarking on a Fitness Odyssey</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Growing up in central Auckland, my life took me from the bustling
            city streets to distant shores and back, but it's the vibrant energy
            of downtown Auckland that I call home. It's here, amidst these
            familiar streets, that my unexpected journey into fitness began.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl mb-3">
            From Reluctant Participant to Fitness Advocate
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            "Adele in the fitness industry? Really?" Thatâ€™s what my friends and
            family used to say. I was the master of excuses when it came to
            sports and PE, and yet, here I am, an enthusiast for the very thing
            I once avoided. The transformation wasn't overnight, but every early
            morning workout (yes, even the dreaded burpees) brought me closer to
            appreciating the power and joy of fitness. I'm proud to be part of
            this world now, where I start my day at the crack of dawn, energised
            and ready.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl mb-3">Finding Strength in My Roots</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            My family's sporting legacy is a tapestry of extraordinary talent -
            from great-grandfathers to cousins who've graced international
            arenas. As for me, I took a different path, one that initially
            skirted the edges of athletic endeavour. But through boxing, I found
            my rhythm, my passion. It wasn't about becoming a champion; it was
            about embracing the discipline, the technique, and the sheer energy
            of the sport.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl mb-3">
            "Fitness is for Everyone" - Adele's Promise
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            "Walking into a gym for the first time can be daunting. I know
            because I've been there. That's why I've created a space where
            everyone belongs, regardless of their fitness level or background.
            Here, it's not about being perfect; it's about being present and
            giving it your all."
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl mb-3">Our Philosophy - Beyond Just Equipment</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our gym might lack the glitz of high-end equipment, but it's
            brimming with something far more valuable - heart and soul. Our
            trainers don't just coach; they inspire. They teach you to tap into
            your inner strength, turning your body into the most powerful
            machine there is. It's an ethos that builds more than just muscle;
            it builds character and camaraderie.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl mb-3">Join Our Community, Find Your Strength</h2>
          <p>
            We're more than just a gym; we're a family. A place where every
            sweat, every laugh, and every challenge shared brings us closer.
            It's not about how you look; it's about how you feel. So, come as
            you are, and let's embark on this fitness journey together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
